# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  LEAF & LENS — DATABASE CONFIGURATION TEMPLATE
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Rename this file to ".env.local" and populate the keys for the
# database engine you choose. The application will dynamically
# switch to whichever engine is configured!
#
# Restart your dev server after modifying this file.
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# 🏆 CHOICE A: TURSO (SQLite / Relational Database)
# 1. Create a free database at https://turso.tech/
# 2. Get your connection URL and Auth Token.
# 3. Paste them below. Tables will be created automatically!
NEXT_PUBLIC_TURSO_DATABASE_URL=libsql://your-db-name.turso.io
NEXT_PUBLIC_TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_turso_auth_token_here

# 🔥 CHOICE B: FIREBASE (Firestore NoSQL + Object Storage)
# 1. Create a free project at https://console.firebase.google.com/
# 2. Enable Firestore & Storage.
# 3. Paste your Web App credentials below.
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your_project_id.firebaseapp.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=your_project_id.appspot.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=your_sender_id
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_APP_ID=your_app_id
